<h2 id="head-5d3ef4b3b3ad677e0b936570c4844b154ddddffe">Mimicry</h2>
<h2 id="head-944b46078941d6bb66dfff0ff43314b8d261d97c">Mimic shapes</h2>
The mimic shapes changed slightly in ToME 2.3.0 and 3.0.0. Information about the 2.2.7 version are available in the <a class="external" href="./www.killerbunnies.org/angband/skill-220.html">ToME 2.2.x Skill Spoiler Page</a>. <p>
For shapeshifting through the Mimicry skill, Level is always the Mimicry skill level and Duration is Mimicry skill@1000 + 50.  
</p>
<p>
A shapeshiftig can be ended by: 
</p>

    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 using the Mimicry power again, 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 the Disperse Magic spell at level 20, 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 the building action <em>Morph restoration</em>. 
</p>
</li>

    </ul>


<h3 id="head-7687a1481d440b21e4dffde2866235d9e617d549">Nature Realm</h3>
<h4 id="head-573dd2c2ed953b97e3c31f3090925fe92109b779">Mouse</h4>
<em>Mice are small, fast and very stealthy</em> 
    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 Available through mimicry while wearing a Mouse Fur 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 Available by quaffing a Morphic Oil [Mouse] 
</p>
</li>

        <ul>

        <li>
<p>
 Level = 2/3 of the character level 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Duration 20 - 40 
</p>
</li>

        </ul>


    <li>
<p>
 Stat mods 
</p>
</li>

        <ul>

  STR -5, DEX +3, CON +1 
        </ul>


    <li>
<p>
 Boni 
</p>
</li>

        <ul>

        <li>
<p>
 Speed + 5 + (level/7) 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Melee to hit bonus + 10 + (level/5) 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Melee to damage bonus is divided by 5. 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Stealth ability + 10 + (level/5) 
</p>
</li>

        </ul>


    <li>
<p>
 Powers 
</p>
</li>

        <ul>

        <li>
<p>
 Invisibility at level 30 
</p>
</li>

        </ul>    </ul>


<h4 id="head-0af99bc6a304e3cb601d31ecdf545bbe6a663826">Eagle</h4>
<em>Eagles are master of the air, good hunters with excellent vision</em> 
    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 Available through mimicry while wearing a Feathers Cloak 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 Available by quaffing a Morphic Oil [Eagle] 
</p>
</li>

        <ul>

        <li>
<p>
 Level = 2/3 of the character level 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Duration 10 - 50 
</p>
</li>

        </ul>


    <li>
<p>
 Stat mods 
</p>
</li>

        <ul>

  STR -3, DEX + 2 + (level/15), CON + 4 + (level/20),   INT -1, WIS +1, CHR -1 
        </ul>


    <li>
<p>
 Boni 
</p>
</li>

        <ul>

        <li>
<p>
 Levitation 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Speed + 2 + (level/6) 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Fly and See Invisible at level 20 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Free Action at level 25 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Resist Electricity at level 30 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Electric Sheet at level 40 
</p>
</li>

        </ul>    </ul>


