<h3 id="head-8d7bf5bf136e81f9388c1f4eca050d6d94e965d7">Others</h3>
<h4 id="head-c61977afa701a7f9e52eaade38164a3d12924e0f">Abomination</h4>
<em>Abominations are failed experiments of powerful wizards.</em> 
    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 Available through mis-used Mimicry powers 
</p>
</li>

        <ul>

        <li>
<p>
 Level = character level 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Duration = 30 
</p>
</li>

        </ul>


    <li>
<p>
 Available through the RBE_ABOMINATION attack 
</p>
</li>

        <ul>

        <li>
<p>
 Level = 50 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Duration = damage of the attack 
</p>
</li>

        </ul>


    <li>
<p>
 Stat mods 
</p>
</li>

        <ul>

  All stats (STR, DEX, INT, WIS, CON, CHR) -10 
        </ul>


    <li>
<p>
 Other effects 
</p>
</li>

        <ul>

        <li>
<p>
 Speed - 10 
</p>
</li>
        <li>
<p>
 Aggravate 
</p>
</li>

        </ul>    </ul>


<h4 id="head-7b9f56b445e86e6a3c8212077d155af244bb66e9">Bear</h4>
